FBIS3-15728 "drsov046_a_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Paris Club Defers Partial Debt Repayment LD0903135794 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 0400 GMT 9 Mar 94 LD0903135794 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] The states that are Russia's creditors, united within the framework of the Paris Club, have agreed to prolong by four months the period of repayment of part of the Russian foreign debt amounting to $15 billion. The postponement applies both to the repayment of part of the credits and to the interest on them. All in all, Russia must repay $2-3 billion during the first four months of this year. However, the Paris Club has not calculated the exact amount yet.
